snippet.title: eFootball - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the first gameplay trailer for eFootball. This gives us a deep dive into eFootball's gameplay mechanics and the experience we can expect on the pitch.

eFootball launches on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and PC this Autumn/Fall. It will also release on iOS and Android soon after. The game is is free-to-play and built in Unreal Engine.

#IGN #Gaming #eFootball
